al; font-size:9pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><a name="_ftn6"></a><a href="#_ftnref6">[6]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt">Union’s concerns over education advisers’ potential conflicts of interest,  BBC new website, </span><a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/education-2075665"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">www.bbc.co.uk/news/education-2075665</span></a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt"> [Accessed 16 December 2013] </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><a name="_ftn7"></a><a href="#_ftnref7">[7]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt"> See Local School Network report at </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt"> </span><a href="http://www.localschoolsnetwork.org.uk/2013/11/private-eye-queries-conflict-of-interest-in-ofsted-inspections-answer-came-there-none/"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.localschoolsnetwork.org.uk/2013/11/private-eye-queries-conflict-of-interest-in-ofsted-inspections-</span><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">answer-came-there-none/</span></a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt"> [Accessed 16 December 2013]. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><a name="_ftn8"></a><a href="#_ftnref8">[8]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt"> </span><a href="http://www.ofsted.gov.uk/inspection-reports/find-inspection-report/provider/ELS/119400"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.ofsted.gov.uk/inspection-reports/find-inspection-report/provider/ELS/119400</span></a></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><a name="_ftn9"></a><a href="#_ftnref9">[9]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt"> Repor</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt">ted in the Guardian, 25.03.13</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt"> </span><a href="http://www.theguardian.com/education/2013/mar/25/ofsted-conerns-academies-undermine-improvement"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.theguardian.com/education/2013/mar/25/ofsted-conerns-academies-undermine-improvement</span></a></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><a name="_ftn10"></a><a href="#_ftnref10">[10]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt">‘County Chief Tells Gove to Halt ‘Academy Broker’ Visits’, </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt">BBC News</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt"> Website, </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt">23</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt"> April 2013, </span><a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/education-22271467"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/education-22271467</span></a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt"> [Accessed 16 January 2013]. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><a name="_ftn11"></a><a href="#_ftnref11">[11]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt">‘</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt">Roke Primary School placed</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt"> in special measures by Ofsted amid teacher exodus ahead of Harris Academy conversion’, </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt">Croydon Guardian,</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt"> 7 June 2013, </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt"> </span><a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/education-22271467"><span style="